	quest.0F914F8C5666E10B.quest_desc: [
		"Welcome to the age of energy (and gregfication XD)"
		""
		"This chapter will focus on introducing energy concepts that will be explored further in future chapters."
		""
		"It's good to maintain good organization and start automating repetitive items like redstone coils."
		""
		"&e-&r Keep in mind that the future of the experience is still long!"
	]
	quest.0F914F8C5666E10B.quest_subtitle: "&5Welcome to Chapter 2"
	quest.0F914F8C5666E10B.title: "Electrical Machinery"
	quest.11927E2D181B985E.quest_subtitle: "&5Get a Clibano Oven"
	quest.11927E2D181B985E.title: "The Clibano Oven"
	quest.123270565A77CAC1.quest_desc: [
		"Thermal Dynamo is the classic heat source generator. Like our old and familiar friend, it generates a considerable amount of energy."
		""
		"It is highly recommended for this chapter, since you won't have access to oil generators."
		""
		"&e-&r Generates &9100 Rf/t&r, consuming &94 mB/t&r of lava."
		""
		"It's important to remember that the thermal dynamo has some face restrictions:"
		""
		"&e-&r Can input fluids on the back."
		"&e-&r Can output energy on the front."
	]
	quest.123270565A77CAC1.quest_subtitle: "&5Craft a Thermal Dynamo"
	quest.123270565A77CAC1.title: "The Classic Lava Generator"
	quest.1333EA4B54BEBCD3.quest_desc: [
		"Tap is a capable of collecting Resin, Maple and Honey."
		""
		"To collect these resources, it is necessary to place it on a specific tree, with a &9Cauldron&r below."
		""
		"&e -&r &9Honey&r: can be collected from beehives and beehives"
		"&e -&r &9Resin&r: can be collected from pine and spruce trees"
		"&e -&r &9Maple&r: can be collected from maple trees"
		"&e -&r the process is slow and takes a long time, the ideal is to place a lot of cauldrons and taps"
	]
