	quest.7218229E14CE6FB3.quest_desc: [
		"Making rubber is a bit tedious and time-consuming, but with the Fluid Extractor, you can save yourself the headache and time."
		""
		"The &9Fluid Extractor&r extracts fluids from the block in front of you. In this case, if you add logs, you'll generate latex."
		""
		"&5>&r How Fluid extractor works"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&9How Fluid Extractor Works&r"
		""
		"It's important to remember that the fluid extractor can break the block in front of it. As it works, you may notice cracks forming in the block. Once it finishes cracking, the block will be broken."
		""
		"&e-&r The Fluid Extractor &9works without power&r, but if it receives power, it will work considerably faster."
		""
		"&5>&r How Latex Processing Unit works"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"&9Latex Processing Unit&r"
		""
		"The latex processing is a machine wich converts fluid latex in latex (item)"
		""
		"&clatex (fluid) + water&r = &alatex (item) &r"
		""
		"&e-&r which can then be converted into rubber."
		"&e-&r With these two machines, you can say goodbye to tedious resin generation and embrace automation with a fluid extractor."
	]
	quest.7218229E14CE6FB3.quest_subtitle: "&5Get a Fluid Extractor and Latex Processing Unit"
	quest.7218229E14CE6FB3.title: "Rubber Factory"
